#: src/uagent/checks.py:19
msgid "Please install Git. Download from: https://git-scm.com/download/win"
msgstr "โปรดติดตั้ง Git ดาวน์โหลดได้ที่: https://git-scm.com/download/win"

#: src/uagent/checks.py:22
msgid "Please install Git. Example: sudo apt install git (Ubuntu/Debian) or sudo yum install git (CentOS/RHEL)"
msgstr "โปรดติดตั้ง Git ตัวอย่าง: sudo apt install git (Ubuntu/Debian) หรือ sudo yum install git (CentOS/RHEL)"

#: src/uagent/checks.py:24
msgid "Please install Git. If using Homebrew: brew install git, or install Xcode Command Line Tools: xcode-select --install"
msgstr "โปรดติดตั้ง Git หากใช้ Homebrew: brew install git หรือ ติดตั้ง Xcode Command Line Tools: xcode-select --install"

#: src/uagent/checks.py:25
msgid "Please install Git. See: https://git-scm.com/"
msgstr "โปรดติดตั้ง Git ดูที่: https://git-scm.com/"

